item.title: CVE-2023-32619|2024-09-26T20:19:58.978Z -- tp-link -- archer%20c50
item.description: Archer C50 firmware versions prior to 'Archer C50(JP)_V3_230505' and Archer C55 firmware versions prior to 'Archer C55(JP)_V1_230506' use hard-coded credentials to login to the affected device, which may allow a network-adjacent unauthenticated attacker to execute an arbitrary OS command.
